work-to-date.md:3:Project folder: `/Users/will/code/ClaudeMeter`
work-to-date.md:7:This project is a macOS 14+ Swift 6 / SwiftUI menu bar app originally named **ClaudeMeter**. It tracks AI service usage limits from the menu bar, using an `@MainActor` observable `AppModel`, actor-isolated services, and Xcode-based build/test workflows.
work-to-date.md:59:The next intended milestone discussed is to make the app its own project and rebrand it as **Pinemeter**.
work-to-date.md:63:- Rename user-facing app identity from ClaudeMeter to Pinemeter.
work-to-date.md:66:- Purge remaining user-facing mentions of ClaudeMeter where they no longer apply.
work-to-date.md:75:- The current app and local instructions still refer heavily to ClaudeMeter and the upstream repository. Rebranding should cover code identifiers, bundle/product names, README/docs, screenshots, About links, workflows, changelog references, and app assets.
work-to-date.md:82:  -project ClaudeMeter.xcodeproj \
work-to-date.md:83:  -scheme ClaudeMeter \
work-to-date.md:89:Create a GSD milestone in this project root for the Pinemeter rebrand with slices roughly ordered as:
work-to-date.md:91:1. Product identity audit: enumerate all ClaudeMeter/upstream references and all user-facing rename targets.
work-to-date.md:92:2. Branding assets: create Pinemeter logo/icon set using Pineit/Pineshot green and white palette.
